Package com.nokia.maps.component.feedback

The feedback package provides a series ofcustom MapComponents which supply feedback to the user, either through offering a callback function to the MIDlet or updating the MapCanvas directly

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FocalEventListener
    This interface defines a callback method for the FocalObserverComponent.
    RestrictMapEventListener
    This interface defines a callback method used by the RestrictMapComponent
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FocalObserverComponent
    This class defines a MapComponent which allows another class to listen for an event which is fired whenever a registered MapObject is moved to the centre of the screen.
    RestrictMapComponent
    View Restriction Component blanks out the Map beyond a given boundary.
    TooltipComponent
    This class defines a MapComponent which associates tooltip text to a MapObject.
